Redistributed Data Notice:

Kanji Time redistributes several data sets under the Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 4.0 International (CC BY-SA 4.0) license. These data sets are included unmodified and retain their original licensing terms:

1. **KanjiDict and KanjiDic2 XML data sets**  
   Source: Electronic Dictionary Research and Development Group (EDRDG)  
   License: CC BY-SA 4.0 (upgraded from 3.0)  
   Website: https://www.edrdg.org/wiki/index.php/KANJIDIC_Project

2. **KanjiVG XML stroke order graphics**  
   Source: Ulrich Apel  
   License: CC BY-SA 4.0 (upgraded from 3.0)  
   Website: https://kanjivg.tagaini.net/

Kanji Time includes an unmodified copy of the Unicode CJKRadicals.txt file. The Unicode data files are freely redistributable under the Unicode License, which permits use in both commercial and non-commercial
applications as long as proper attribution is given.

1. **Unicode CJK Radicals**
   Source: Unicode Consortium  
   License: Unicode License Version 3.0  
   Website: https://www.unicode.org/Public/15.1.0/ucd/CJKRadicals.txt  

All redistributed data remains in its original form. All rights remain with the original authors and licensors. By using this software, you agree to comply with the terms of these third-party licences when accessing or redistributing the included data.

